channel.topic:
Design your own custom adventure!
Challenge dates: August 18, 2020 – August 31, 2020 at 6 PM PT

messages.content:
:adventure_crystals: Custom Adventure Build Challenge! :adventure_crystals: 

Adventures! You’ve activated them to defeat mobs o’ plenty, mine epic treasure, and solve all the other wacky puzzles the game designers thought of. We know your minds are brimming with equally zany and  adventurey ideas and we want to see them in real life!

:adventures: How? **Design your own custom adventure!** Grab any size buildplate, use any and all blocks in your inventory, and place your favorite friendly or not-so friendly mobs.

Your creations should be just as fun in regular and life-size play modes. ↕️ Will you build high or low? 🧩 Puzzley contraptions? ⚔️ Hordes of mobs? 🆕 Something totally new? Now’s your time to shine—shine bright like an adventure crystal!

:timer: Challenge dates: August 18, 2020 – August 31, 2020 at 6 PM PT

__Challenge Guidelines__
:earth: Your creation must be built entirely by you and in Minecraft Earth.
:crafting_table: Your build must be a brand new creation, crafted just for this challenge.
:buildplate: Build your imagination! Challenge theme is open to interpretation and buildplate size won’t be a factor in judging.
:sign: Post your images or video submission and buildplate share link in #custom-adventure-challenge by the end date. Feel free to ask a Moderator to pin it!
:challenges_og: Submissions may be used in social media posts.
:fast_parrot: Have fun!
